mpact-ring-battery-plus-doorbell-deals-sales</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-22T12:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-22T12:00:00-05:00</updated><title>谷歌浏览器的新人工智能可以帮你完成句子</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;插图描绘了 Google Chrome 的“帮我写”工具的各个方面。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xBEAQH2sYhMNxtiJpAC41pKjIoQ=/0x10:1920x1290/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73156844/Google_help_me_write_image_hed.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;当您懒得自己填写网络表单时，可以提供一些额外的帮助。&lt;/em>; |图片：Google&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;bjkzsz&quot;>;Google 已开始推出“帮助我写作”——一项实验性&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12 /6/23990466/google-gemini-llm-ai-model&quot;>;Gemini 驱动的 Chrome 浏览器的生成 AI 功能，旨在帮助用户根据网页内容编写或优化文本。继周二稳定发布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://groups.google.com/g/discuss-webrtc/c/Gc5vmA5ry20?pli=1&quot;>;Chrome M122&lt;/a>; 之后，新的写作助手现已推出美国英语 Chrome 用户可以在 Mac 和 Windows PC 上试用。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;yWcr7k&quot;>;“帮我写作”重点是提供简短内容的写作建议，例如填写数字调查和评论、查询产品信息或起草在线销售商品的描述。谷歌表示，该工具可以“了解您所在网页的上下文”，将相关信息纳入其建议中——例如，突出显示...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2024/2/22/24079906/google-chrome-help-me-write-gemini-ai-tool-finish-sentences&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/22/24079906/google-chrome-help-me-write-gemini-ai-tool-finish-sentences" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/22/24079906/google-chrome-help-me-write-gemini-ai-tool-finish-sentences</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-22T12:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-22T12:00:00-05:00</updated><title>推销员的诞生</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手机录制产品视频评论。屏幕前是一堆包装纸、盒子，产品散落一地。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com /thumbor/dpLgP8RlJ9ji5SCLHBUS7UQvG8c=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73156858/246997_Flip_shopping_app_AKrales_0012.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Ame 拍摄lia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption >; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Flip 购物应用程序是 TikTok 的仿制品，仅包含赚取附属收入的视频。一个月来，我尝试影响陌生人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24078625/flip-influencers-tiktok-shopping-product-reviews-monetization&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24078625/flip-influencers-tiktok-shopping-product-reviews-monetization" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24078625/flip-influencers-tiktok-shopping-product-reviews-monetization</id><author><name>佐藤米娅</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-22T11:30:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-22T11:30:00-05:00</updated><title> Riot 的英雄联盟战士现在称为 2XKO</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;两个 2XKO 角色的图像：Ekko 是一个有着深色皮肤和白色长发绺的非洲男人，旁边是 Ahri 是一个浅色皮肤的女人，有着深蓝色的头发和狐狸耳朵。两个角色都向观众伸出手来。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RxJ9CuDV8F0ElncZ0fETl93NGgU=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73156779/2XKO_KeyArt_Ahri_Ekko_1920x1080 _Final__1_.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Riot Games&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ixZQTz&quot;>;Riot Games 为其正在开发的 2v2 格斗游戏 &lt;em>;Project L&lt;/em>; 赋予了正式名称：&lt; em>;2XKO&lt;/em>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZBJcRo&quot;>;&lt;em>;2XKO&lt;/em>; — 这个名字不太可能产生自己的流行语 ala &lt;a href=&quot;https://knowyourmeme .com/memes/whens-mahvel&quot;>;“Mahvel 什么时候上映？”&lt;/a>; — &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/15/20915338/league-of-legends-animated -series-fighting-game-cards-arcane-runeterra-project-l-trailers&quot;>;于 2019 年首次公布&lt;/a>;，同时还有一系列其他&lt;em>;联盟&lt;/em>;主题项目，包括&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22763818/netflix-league-of-legends-arcane-review&quot;>;&lt;em>;奥术&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;和&lt;em>;符文之地传奇&lt;/em>;。然而，去年，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/22/24047568/riot-games-league-of-legends-forge-runeterra-layoffs&quot;>;Riot 裁员约500 人&lt;/a>;，缩减包括 &lt;em>;Runeterra&lt;/em>; 在内的项目，并关闭其出版部门 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/12/5/20993328/riot-forge -publishing-label-league-of-legends-games&quot;>;Riot Forge&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;CCCOOf&quot;>;自首次发布以来，Riot 提供了零星的开发更新，最终在游戏的第一手版本中达到顶峰-EVO 2023 上的演示。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;c0LYZP&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;position:relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%;&quot;>; &lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pi2ReE&quot;>;&lt;em>;2XKO&lt;/em>; 是一款 2v2 格斗游戏，但与其他双打格斗游戏（例如 &lt;em>;Marvel vs. Capcom&lt;/em>;）不同， &lt;em>;2XKO&lt;/em>;让您可以竞争或合作地进行游戏。玩家可以组队...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/22/24079608/project-l-2kxo-fighting-game-league-of-图例&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/22/24079608/project-l-2kxo-fighting-game-league-of-legends" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/22/24079608/project-l-2kxo-fighting-game-league-of-legends</id><author><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-22T09:42:18-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-22T09:42:18-05:00</updated><title>最终幻想 VII 重生：所有新闻和更新</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《最终幻想 VII：重生》的屏幕截图，其中标志性反派萨菲罗斯背对着观众，全身被火焰包围。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/cB-_Nz34RbzBynekvq5FNmzTI9c=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73156490/EN_06_FF7REBIRTH_Demo.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Square Enix&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;在《重生》中，我们的英雄将探索米德加之外的世界。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/24078609/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-news-updates-trailers&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24078609/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-news-updates-trailers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24078609/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-news-updates-trailers</id><author><na